    <item>
      <title>潮湿天气影响业绩，Fevertree 股价跌至八年来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/fevertree-slumps-to-eight-year-low-as-wet-weather-rains-on-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于业绩受到恶劣天气的影响，高端滋补品制造商 Fevertree Drinks Plc 的股价跌至八年来的最低点，该公司大幅下调了年度销售增长预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/fevertree-slumps-to-eight-year-low-as-wet-weather-rains-on-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 10:19:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴伐利亚州探索将 Mpox 疫苗供应量增加 5000 万的方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/bavarian-explores-options-to-boost-mpox-jab-supply-by-50-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴伐利亚北欧公司 (Bavarian Nordic A/S) 是少数几家获得批准生产 mpox 疫苗的公司之一，该公司正在增加疫苗供应数量，以应对非洲的疫情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/bavarian-explores-options-to-boost-mpox-jab-supply-by-50-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 10:16:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
